7. Build & run
docker build -t flask-orm-demo .
docker run -p 5000:5000 flask-orm-demo

or:
podman build   --platform linux/arm/v7   --network host   -t flask-orm-demo:armv7 .

for cross compiling:
apt-get install python3-librouteros
apt-get install python3-flask
apt install qemu-user-static
systemctl --user restart podman



8. Endpoints overview
HTML

GET / – Home
GET /items – List items
GET /add – Add item
GET /system-call – Runs echo hello world
REST API
GET /api/items
POST /api/items
{ "name": "Example item" }
DELETE /api/items/<id>
